item.dc:creator: @The_Reaper_X The Reaper X
item.description:
@The_Reaper_X wrote:

[quote=“wat72, post:4, topic:260673”][quote author=SpiritSim link=topic=344226.msg2656969#msg2656969 date=1233941162]
It says The server Arminazo-Scape is offline, it must be online before you can register it here. How to put it online i am new i only created my server today can some one please help Thanks.
[/quote]You created a server, yet you haven’t even gotten it online? You must mean you downloaded a server.[/quote]He’s trying to put his server on a server status page.

Like Digital said, open your source folder and click run.bat. You’re going to have to give them your IP adress, unless you’ve set up a domain via no-ip.com
